It has Some parallax effect, over two hundred shortcodes, compatibility with WPML for translation and mega menu. Documentation and support are also on point for you to never feel lonely on your journey to a victorious launch of your online space.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"color: #000; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 40px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Jevelin\"><\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/jevelin.shufflehound.com\/hello\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow noreferrer\">Jevelin<\/a><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-6970\" src=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Jevelin-Wordpress-theme.png\" alt=\"Jevelin WordPress Theme\" width=\"1350\" height=\"604\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Jevelin-Wordpress-theme.png 1350w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Jevelin-Wordpress-theme-300x134.png 300w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Jevelin-Wordpress-theme-768x344.png 768w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Jevelin-Wordpress-theme-1024x458.png 1024w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Jevelin-Wordpress-theme-600x268.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1350px) 100vw, 1350px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Jevelin is supremely flexible and its skillset includes premium plugins like the Slider Revolution and Contact Form 7 that can make your landing pages both dynamic and functional within a few clicks and in no time. Or you can also install numerous landing page templates with a single click. It has efficient HTML5 and CSS3 coding and styling which makes it lightweight, fast-loading theme that performs smoothly under all traffic conditions.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"color: #000; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 40px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" i